## ðŸ“ Naming Conventions

- **Components:** PascalCase (e.g., `UserProfile.tsx`, `SubmitButton.tsx`).
- **Hooks:** camelCase, must start with `use` (e.g., `useAuth.ts`).
- **Functions/Variables:** camelCase (e.g., `handleSubmit`, `isLoading`).
- **Types/Interfaces:** PascalCase (e.g., `User`, `AuthResponse`).
- **Constants:** UPPER_SNAKE_CASE (e.g., `MAX_RETRY_COUNT`).

